After-school activities!

What to do after school? You don't know? Then check this out!

Welcome to the map that helps you find cool spots to visit after school, by yourself or with friends! Check the info box in the right lower corner for more information.
Follow the instructions below to navigate the map:

  1. You can explore the map by panning with the mouse. To zoom, use the mouse wheel or the + and – buttons in the top-left corner.
  2. Locate your school on the map and click on it. If you cannot find it, use the search bar.
  3. After clicking on the school the available services within just a 15 min and routes to them will appear on the map.
  4. Then you can click on the displayed services to get more information about them.
  5. Great! Now you know everything you need. Have funbrowsing the map and go check your friends' schools aswell!
